include ../../../templates/mixins.pug

+breadcrumbs("What's My Business Worth?", 'Established Business',
  [
    ['Home', '/'],
    ["What's My Business Worth?", '/calculator/selectYourBusiness'],
    ["Established Business", '']
  ]
)

.container.calculator-container
  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6
      .warning-block.m0
        i.fa.fa-exclamation-triangle 
        span.warning-text 
          | There are two types of securities your business can issue on GrowthFountain: 
          b Common Equity
          | &nbsp;or&nbsp;
          b Revenue Share.

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6.mt45
      p
        b Common Equity
        | represents an ownership share in your business. Common Equity might make sense for you if you expect to reinvest the cash flow your business generates to fund additional growth.

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6.text-sm-center.mt25
      a(href="/calculator/establishedBusiness/intro").btn.btn-primary.text-uppercase Established Business Valuation Calculator

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6.mt45
      p 
        b PayBack Share &nbsp;
        | is a GrowthFountain created revenue sharing security; it is a form of investment contract in which the Company shares 5% of its revenue annually with investors.

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6.text-xs-center.mt25
      a(href="/calculator/paybackshare/step-1").btn.btn-primary.text-uppercase revenue share calculator
